WEBVTT

01:32.060 --> 01:35.030
[How dare you!?]

01:35.090 --> 01:37.940
[Episode 3]

01:42.470 --> 01:44.390
What I meant was

01:44.759 --> 01:47.350
that my temper is indeed terrible.

01:48.039 --> 01:49.170
Please sit, Mother.

01:49.479 --> 01:51.380
Mother, why get angry

01:51.710 --> 01:52.840
over a mere consort?

01:53.350 --> 01:54.479
Here, have some tea.

01:54.759 --> 01:56.289
Let's talk things through.

02:00.000 --> 02:01.200
Little Crown Prince,

02:01.350 --> 02:02.950
how are your studies lately?

02:03.230 --> 02:03.640
F-

02:04.400 --> 02:05.560
Father...

02:07.280 --> 02:07.920
recently

02:08.590 --> 02:10.720
m-my studies have been satisfactory.

02:11.120 --> 02:11.910
Very good!

02:13.000 --> 02:15.260
Thanks to Mother's virtuous influence,

02:15.430 --> 02:18.090
the little Crown Prince
has been raised so well.

02:18.470 --> 02:19.590
Little Crown Prince,

02:19.590 --> 02:21.430
if you need anything in the future,

02:21.430 --> 02:22.710
feel free to tell me.

02:23.630 --> 02:24.120
Yes.

02:24.910 --> 02:27.110
Now you're acting like a proper father.

02:29.000 --> 02:30.520
There is indeed something

02:31.310 --> 02:33.680
you can help the Crown Prince with.

02:34.800 --> 02:36.280
Our Crown Prince

02:36.590 --> 02:38.520
is exceptionally intelligent.

02:39.310 --> 02:42.520
However, his horsemanship
and archery skills

02:42.840 --> 02:44.100
are somewhat lacking.

02:45.710 --> 02:48.630
Doesn't General Luo have a young son

02:49.310 --> 02:50.630
of similar age?

02:51.630 --> 02:53.710
Why not summon him to the palace

02:54.680 --> 02:56.740
to be a companion to the Crown Prince?

02:57.360 --> 02:58.190
General Luo

02:59.000 --> 03:01.200
has just been commended for his merits.

03:01.240 --> 03:02.630
Wouldn't this be somewhat...

03:02.630 --> 03:03.150
Guards!

03:04.430 --> 03:05.360
Here we go again.

03:05.470 --> 03:07.470
I'll draft the decree immediately.

03:11.120 --> 03:12.120
Guards!

03:14.470 --> 03:17.000
Serve tea to Consort Yu.

03:21.280 --> 03:22.140
Your Highness.

03:22.680 --> 03:23.740
What are you doing?

03:24.000 --> 03:24.860
Your Highness,

03:25.190 --> 03:27.520
I was blessed with a son
only in my forties.

03:27.710 --> 03:28.840
He is my life.

03:29.840 --> 03:31.590
Now, His Majesty summoning him
to the palace—

03:31.590 --> 03:32.680
while it sounds like
making him a study partner,

03:32.680 --> 03:34.400
in reality,
it's actually holding him as hostage.

03:34.400 --> 03:35.190
What if...

03:35.840 --> 03:37.800
What if he fails
to please the Crown Prince?

03:37.800 --> 03:39.130
If anything goes wrong,

03:40.120 --> 03:42.320
it could cost my entire family's lives!

03:42.870 --> 03:43.600
General Luo,

03:45.120 --> 03:46.320
please rise to speak.

03:50.560 --> 03:53.560
I was a companion
to the Crown Prince since childhood.

03:54.680 --> 03:56.079
The hardships involved,

03:57.000 --> 03:59.000
no one understands better than I do.

04:02.280 --> 04:03.010
General Luo,

04:04.240 --> 04:05.870
if you still trust me,

04:08.110 --> 04:09.310
give me some time.

04:10.030 --> 04:11.750
I promise to bring your child back

04:11.750 --> 04:13.240
safe and sound.

04:14.030 --> 04:15.630
Your Highness is most gracious.

04:15.630 --> 04:16.959
I am but a simple warrior

04:17.310 --> 04:18.839
and don't know fancy words.

04:19.190 --> 04:20.750
If you can save my beloved son,

04:20.750 --> 04:22.010
I will lay down my life,

04:22.270 --> 04:22.870
and follow

04:23.310 --> 04:24.240
your lead alone.

04:25.800 --> 04:27.330
Rest assured, General Luo.

04:27.720 --> 04:29.190
I will keep my promise.

04:30.310 --> 04:30.750
I shall

04:31.070 --> 04:32.070
take my leave now.

04:50.510 --> 04:51.840
I've only just realized

04:52.430 --> 04:55.000
why you suddenly came
to the Empress Dowager today

04:55.000 --> 04:56.200
and put on such a show.

04:56.950 --> 04:57.590
What show?

04:58.480 --> 05:00.690
You wanted everyone in the palace to know

05:00.690 --> 05:01.950
that you won't tolerate me
being criticised,

05:01.950 --> 05:03.600
let alone being framed.

05:04.240 --> 05:05.500
This way they'll think

05:06.360 --> 05:09.120
this demonic consort has become
the emperor's weakness.

05:09.120 --> 05:11.380
Controlling her means controlling you.

05:11.720 --> 05:12.800
This would make them lower their guard

05:12.800 --> 05:14.430
while they continue fighting
among themselves.

05:14.430 --> 05:17.030
This way we can develop our strength
in secret.

05:17.070 --> 05:17.470
Right?

05:19.390 --> 05:20.590
You figured that out?

05:21.800 --> 05:23.000
Is my acting that bad?

05:23.240 --> 05:24.770
Your acting was excellent.

05:25.040 --> 05:27.100
It took me a whole day to figure it out.

05:27.720 --> 05:29.250
You're truly a mastermind.

05:30.560 --> 05:33.420
Now I've become both your shield
and your weakness.

05:33.750 --> 05:34.680
When one day,

05:35.070 --> 05:35.870
an assassin

05:36.830 --> 05:37.870
holds a sword

05:38.360 --> 05:40.420
against my throat to force your hand,

05:40.480 --> 05:41.540
you could just say,

05:41.920 --> 05:42.650
"What a fool.

05:42.920 --> 05:44.250
I don't care about her."

05:44.630 --> 05:45.830
Then with one stroke,

05:46.120 --> 05:49.050
skewer both me and the assassin
like candied fruits.

05:51.120 --> 05:52.720
If you really think that way,

05:53.950 --> 05:54.950
aren't you angry?

05:55.560 --> 05:56.390
Not at all.

05:59.430 --> 06:00.960
We're all drowning people.

06:01.480 --> 06:03.920
Whoever can swim to safety
does so by their own ability.

06:03.920 --> 06:05.380
I understand completely.

06:05.680 --> 06:06.920
I'd do the same in your position.

06:06.920 --> 06:07.600
Besides,

06:08.110 --> 06:09.390
didn't I not let him know
about Prince Duan

06:09.390 --> 06:10.850
contacting me in private?

06:11.190 --> 06:11.790
Moreover,

06:12.240 --> 06:15.000
my request to go to the library
was also self-serving.

06:15.000 --> 06:17.360
The two doors there connect
the inside and outside of the palace,

06:17.360 --> 06:19.510
providing my escape route from this place.

06:19.510 --> 06:21.310
But let's be clear about one thing.

06:21.310 --> 06:23.310
Don't give me that
self-sacrifice nonsense.

06:23.310 --> 06:25.430
If someday only one of us can survive,

06:25.870 --> 06:28.270
don't go easy on me
just because I'm a woman.

06:28.360 --> 06:29.960
I won't go easy on you either.

06:31.950 --> 06:32.810
No matter what,

06:33.510 --> 06:34.840
I will never betray you.

06:38.800 --> 06:39.730
Even if in the end

06:40.070 --> 06:41.400
you choose Prince Duan,

06:41.480 --> 06:42.940
it would still be the same.

06:43.510 --> 06:44.110
Of course,

06:45.120 --> 06:47.050
if you don't want to choose anyone,

06:48.159 --> 06:49.430
if someday I die first,

06:50.240 --> 06:51.040
before I die,

06:51.830 --> 06:53.510
I'll send you out of the palace,

06:53.510 --> 06:55.370
away from this place of conflict,

06:55.830 --> 06:58.030
toward the freedom that belongs to you.

07:01.950 --> 07:04.010
No one will harm you in the slightest.

07:04.430 --> 07:04.890
I swear.

07:10.920 --> 07:12.630
That's all far in the future.

07:14.000 --> 07:15.070
Let's first

07:16.000 --> 07:18.060
handle the immediate matters at hand

07:18.360 --> 07:20.420
and enjoy the moonlight while we can.

07:40.630 --> 07:42.310
The moon is so full tonight.

07:42.750 --> 07:44.210
Because today is the 15th.

07:45.630 --> 07:46.310
I see.

07:49.390 --> 07:50.070
The

07:50.830 --> 07:51.360
15th...

08:00.560 --> 08:01.090
Yong'er.

08:09.310 --> 08:09.770
My lord.

08:12.720 --> 08:13.870
I haven't seen you for days.

08:13.870 --> 08:15.270
Why have you lost weight?

08:15.480 --> 08:16.740
Did something happen?

08:18.360 --> 08:19.630
Nothing serious.

08:21.040 --> 08:22.070
Just today,

08:22.270 --> 08:26.360
when Consort Zhuang and Consort Yu went to
pay respects to the Empress Dowager,

08:26.360 --> 08:28.020
I teased Consort Yu a few times

08:28.800 --> 08:30.530
and was slapped by His Majesty.

08:31.000 --> 08:32.059
One must be careful

08:32.630 --> 08:34.960
in the harem about everything these days.

08:35.000 --> 08:35.799
I'm scared...

08:36.630 --> 08:37.890
Scared that one day...

08:40.200 --> 08:41.630
You took such a great risk

08:42.669 --> 08:44.440
to entrust your true feelings to me.

08:44.440 --> 08:45.500
As long as I am here,

08:46.840 --> 08:48.770
I won't let anything happen to you.

08:56.550 --> 08:58.010
Actually, these few days,

08:58.510 --> 09:00.390
I've been carrying the sachet you gave me

09:00.390 --> 09:00.960
on me.

09:02.200 --> 09:02.930
When I see it,

09:03.750 --> 09:04.950
it's like seeing you.

09:05.750 --> 09:07.480
We staked out an hour in advance

09:07.720 --> 09:08.780
just to eavesdrop?

09:09.320 --> 09:11.320
This isn't just any eavesdropping.

09:11.790 --> 09:12.600
The book says

09:13.910 --> 09:16.170
that their first date on a full moon night

09:16.480 --> 09:17.910
laid the foundation for

09:18.390 --> 09:20.200
years of cooperation between the leads.

09:20.200 --> 09:21.720
Do you remember how I died?

09:22.480 --> 09:23.870
-Seriously—
-Stop complaining.

09:23.870 --> 09:25.330
I can't hear anything now.

09:30.390 --> 09:30.990
By the way,

09:31.670 --> 09:33.910
why hasn't Your Highness
sent any news for days?

09:33.910 --> 09:35.840
Are you busy with official duties?

09:37.360 --> 09:38.360
It's a long story.

09:38.840 --> 09:40.900
Why did they change locations again?

09:44.080 --> 09:45.880
Why did she leave just like this?

09:47.600 --> 09:49.550
Recently, the affairs at my residence
have been troublesome.

09:49.550 --> 09:51.410
I truly have little leisure time.

09:51.510 --> 09:53.170
It's related to the harem too.

09:53.630 --> 09:55.630
Actually, I risked coming to see you

09:55.630 --> 09:56.960
because of this matter.

09:58.240 --> 10:00.670
The connection between women
in the harem and the court

10:00.670 --> 10:02.490
is always about their family background.

10:02.490 --> 10:04.620
If it makes Your Highness so hesitant,

10:04.630 --> 10:06.830
it must be either Consort Shu's brother

10:07.360 --> 10:09.090
or Noble Consort Wei's father.

10:10.960 --> 10:12.510
You are indeed clever.

10:13.960 --> 10:15.150
It is indeed Grand Tutor Wei.

10:15.150 --> 10:16.080
Grand Tutor Wei.

10:17.120 --> 10:18.780
A key character has appeared.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.720
Grand Tutor Wei's son recently

10:23.720 --> 10:26.550
trampled a commoner to death
with his horse in the street.

10:26.550 --> 10:29.550
The victim had come to the capital
to file an imperial complaint

10:29.550 --> 10:32.150
against the Salt Inspector
from his hometown.

10:36.550 --> 10:38.360
Intercepting an imperial complaint

10:38.360 --> 10:39.420
is a serious crime.

10:39.600 --> 10:41.750
The scoundrel knew he had committed
a terrible offense

10:41.750 --> 10:42.910
that couldn't be undone,

10:42.910 --> 10:45.120
so he privately contacted Grand Tutor Wei.

10:45.120 --> 10:46.720
Grand Tutor Wei, eager to protect his son,

10:46.720 --> 10:48.520
managed to suppress the matter.

10:48.790 --> 10:51.030
Grand Tutor Wei
is the Empress Dowager's man.

10:51.030 --> 10:52.030
Noble Consort Wei

10:52.270 --> 10:54.200
is also highly favored because of this.

10:54.200 --> 10:56.660
He is
the Empress Dowager's right-hand man.

10:58.240 --> 11:01.000
For years, he's been using
the Salt Transportation License

11:01.000 --> 11:03.800
to amass wealth
and commit all kinds of evil deeds.

11:04.320 --> 11:05.250
What goes around

11:07.000 --> 11:08.630
comes around.

11:13.390 --> 11:16.070
That's exactly how it's written
in the original novel?

11:16.070 --> 11:17.200
Word for word.

11:19.390 --> 11:21.920
The author must be
an "Infernal Affairs" fan?

11:23.840 --> 11:26.170
Where's the straw mat for your lower body?

11:30.150 --> 11:32.010
This imperial palace is too poor.

11:32.080 --> 11:33.010
Come in quickly.

11:41.440 --> 11:43.200
Your Highness need not say more.

11:43.200 --> 11:44.660
Tell me what you want to do.

11:45.200 --> 11:48.030
I want to take this opportunity
to eliminate Grand Tutor Wei

11:48.030 --> 11:49.830
and bring justice to the people.

11:51.440 --> 11:53.510
But this matter is of great importance,

11:53.510 --> 11:55.320
and I haven't figured out a good plan yet.

11:55.320 --> 11:56.600
I know a good way.

11:58.150 --> 11:59.210
The Salt Inspector

11:59.480 --> 12:00.270
once gave

12:00.600 --> 12:02.720
Grand Tutor Wei a sarira as a bribe.

12:03.750 --> 12:04.750
-But he thought...
-Look. Is it beautiful?

12:04.750 --> 12:06.550
It is just an ordinary red agate,

12:07.390 --> 12:10.080
so he gave it to his daughter,
Noble Consort Wei.

12:11.910 --> 12:13.320
How did you learn of this?

12:13.480 --> 12:14.280
It's a secret.

12:15.550 --> 12:16.070
Anyway,

12:17.080 --> 12:18.410
I will find a way to get it

12:19.150 --> 12:20.120
to help you.

12:25.870 --> 12:26.530
Yong'er...

12:29.030 --> 12:30.030
If that's true,

12:31.960 --> 12:33.760
you'll be doing me a great favor.

12:39.600 --> 12:40.480
What a jerk.

12:41.480 --> 12:43.280
Playing Xie Yong'er like a fool.

12:44.600 --> 12:47.330
You're really getting into
this eavesdropping.

12:49.030 --> 12:50.670
That relic they mentioned,

12:52.200 --> 12:53.200
is it really true?

12:54.030 --> 12:55.030
It should be real.

12:59.080 --> 12:59.610
Let's go.

13:02.360 --> 13:03.840
Xie Yong'er is willing to do anything—

13:03.840 --> 13:05.480
even theft—for Prince Duan.

13:05.840 --> 13:06.910
She's really going all out.

13:06.910 --> 13:08.030
You stepped on my foot.

13:08.030 --> 13:08.960
I-I'm sorry.

13:11.870 --> 13:12.600
Who's there?

13:23.480 --> 13:24.280
Your Majesty.

13:24.390 --> 13:25.250
Your Highness.

13:27.670 --> 13:29.360
Did His Majesty and Consort Yu

13:29.550 --> 13:31.550
have a fight in the Imperial Garden?

13:34.080 --> 13:35.340
Why are you so gossipy?

13:40.720 --> 13:43.120
I can't believe our plan
to drive them apart

13:43.390 --> 13:44.320
actually...

13:45.480 --> 13:46.790
Worked!

13:48.360 --> 13:49.090
Who's there?

13:52.030 --> 13:52.630
My Prince,

13:53.120 --> 13:53.650
it was me.

13:55.510 --> 13:56.750
He didn't report us.

13:56.910 --> 13:57.750
He even

13:58.200 --> 13:59.120
covered for us.

14:00.120 --> 14:02.320
If I'd known I was so good at recruiting,

14:02.510 --> 14:04.140
I should have gone into HR.

14:04.200 --> 14:04.960
In that case,

14:05.870 --> 14:07.150
Xu Yao switching sides

14:08.000 --> 14:09.330
is just a matter of time.

14:09.630 --> 14:11.000
Taking down Prince Duan

14:11.550 --> 14:13.080
is not far from succeeding.

14:18.840 --> 14:20.840
When Grand Tutor Wei is imprisoned,

14:21.510 --> 14:24.600
Xu Yao will surely use the opportunity
to investigate his father's case.

14:24.600 --> 14:27.260
He might even sneak in
to question him directly.

14:27.270 --> 14:29.670
Then I should get there before him
to question him—

14:29.670 --> 14:31.030
to take control of the situation.

14:31.030 --> 14:32.080
This Prince Duan

14:32.390 --> 14:33.510
is not a fool.

14:34.080 --> 14:35.080
Once he finds out,

14:35.630 --> 14:37.030
Xu Yao might be in danger.

14:37.630 --> 14:38.600
Then I'll create

14:38.600 --> 14:40.000
a new career change plan for him.

14:40.000 --> 14:41.930
He can get land allocation rewards

14:41.970 --> 14:43.240
based on his own merit.

14:43.670 --> 14:44.840
Full benefits,

14:45.240 --> 14:46.270
annual leave, and paternity leave—

14:46.270 --> 14:47.600
line them all up for him.

14:50.750 --> 14:52.360
Then I can't sleep here tonight.

14:52.360 --> 14:52.670
Why?

14:53.000 --> 14:53.870
Xie Yong'er is going to

14:53.870 --> 14:55.550
go steal
Noble Consort Wei's sarira bead tomorrow.

14:55.550 --> 14:56.950
I need to be in the palace.

14:57.200 --> 14:57.860
Otherwise,

14:58.440 --> 14:59.440
with no audience,

15:00.240 --> 15:02.040
who will the actors perform for?

15:05.600 --> 15:07.800
How about a couple more special drinks?

15:07.910 --> 15:10.970
Nope. Drinking too much
will interfere with business.

15:12.550 --> 15:14.480
Help! There's a thief!

15:16.000 --> 15:16.270
One.

15:16.600 --> 15:16.860
Two.

15:17.600 --> 15:18.000
Three.

15:18.280 --> 15:21.030
[Changning Palace]

15:18.510 --> 15:18.850
Four.

15:19.600 --> 15:19.930
Five.

15:20.440 --> 15:20.700
Six.

15:21.270 --> 15:21.670
Seven.

15:21.910 --> 15:23.510
My Lady, bad news!

15:23.720 --> 15:24.000
Two.

15:24.480 --> 15:24.880
Three.

15:25.320 --> 15:25.650
Four.

15:26.240 --> 15:26.570
Five.

15:27.080 --> 15:27.360
Six.

15:27.910 --> 15:28.550
My Lady!

15:28.790 --> 15:30.630
Something valuable went missing
from Noble Consort Wei's palace.

15:30.630 --> 15:31.870
They're searching everywhere for it.

15:31.870 --> 15:33.600
Concubine Xie is also spreading rumors.

15:33.600 --> 15:35.480
She's saying you must be involved
in this matter.

15:35.480 --> 15:36.720
Isn't that a malicious accusation?

15:36.720 --> 15:37.120
Eight.

15:37.320 --> 15:38.320
My Lady!

15:38.600 --> 15:38.840
Two.

15:38.840 --> 15:40.510
Are you listening to me?

15:42.480 --> 15:42.810
Five.

15:43.670 --> 15:44.080
Four.

15:45.150 --> 15:45.600
Three.

15:46.790 --> 15:47.080
Two.

15:48.960 --> 15:49.240
One.

15:50.360 --> 15:52.120
The treasure I've lost is priceless.

15:52.120 --> 15:55.180
Ten of your lives wouldn't be enough
for me to pay for it.

15:57.200 --> 15:58.790
You few, search the back courtyard.

15:58.790 --> 16:00.520
The rest of you, search inside.

16:09.790 --> 16:11.480
Your Highness, we haven't found anything.

16:11.480 --> 16:12.360
Useless fools.

16:13.320 --> 16:14.450
I'll search myself.

16:15.240 --> 16:16.570
Sister, let me help you.

16:19.750 --> 16:20.550
Nothing here?

16:22.910 --> 16:23.610
Oh, Sister.

16:23.910 --> 16:24.710
Come quickly.

16:27.150 --> 16:29.150
There's a hidden compartment here.

16:29.870 --> 16:32.130
But I'm certain there's nothing inside.

16:39.890 --> 16:40.950
By the way, Sister.

16:41.390 --> 16:43.080
There are 10 more chests over there.

16:43.080 --> 16:44.200
There are 6 cabinets there

16:44.200 --> 16:45.260
and 3 makeup boxes.

16:45.270 --> 16:46.110
Let's search them all carefully.

16:46.110 --> 16:51.720
[Changning Palace]

16:47.630 --> 16:48.090
Sister!

16:48.630 --> 16:50.440
Are you not going to search anymore?

16:50.440 --> 16:52.170
Hasn't anyone found anything?

16:52.790 --> 16:54.050
All of you are useless!

16:54.390 --> 16:55.200
Your Highness.

16:55.200 --> 16:55.860
We found it.

16:56.240 --> 16:58.370
There's a hidden compartment in here.

16:59.670 --> 17:00.440
Yu Wanyin.

17:00.870 --> 17:02.870
What do you have to say for yourself?

17:03.000 --> 17:04.329
Caught you red-handed.

17:04.550 --> 17:05.010
Guards!

17:05.400 --> 17:06.210
Arrest her!

17:06.349 --> 17:07.750
I'd like to see who dares.

17:09.640 --> 17:12.700
-Greetings, Your Majesty.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

17:13.960 --> 17:16.490
Shouldn't he be attending court
at this hour?

17:20.829 --> 17:21.550
Surprised?

17:22.200 --> 17:22.930
I left early.

17:27.480 --> 17:28.359
Your Majesty.

17:28.920 --> 17:30.520
Please don't blame Lady Wei.

17:30.960 --> 17:33.030
She lost a rare treasure.

17:33.400 --> 17:34.480
She's too anxious.

17:35.310 --> 17:36.310
that's why she's

17:36.310 --> 17:38.510
blindly taking her anger out on me.

17:39.480 --> 17:40.280
Your Majesty.

17:40.400 --> 17:41.590
Don't listen to her nonsense.

17:41.590 --> 17:42.520
I have evidence.

17:42.830 --> 17:44.290
Someone saw a young eunuch

17:44.310 --> 17:45.270
steal my agate,

17:45.480 --> 17:47.400
and deliver it to Consort Yu's palace.

17:47.400 --> 17:48.200
Bring it here!

18:04.230 --> 18:05.030
Your Majesty!

18:05.160 --> 18:07.000
Is this your so-called evidence?

18:07.000 --> 18:07.880
This is impossible.

18:07.880 --> 18:08.940
It was clearly a...

18:08.960 --> 18:10.070
It was clearly a precious pearl.

18:10.070 --> 18:11.530
How did it turn into a date?

18:19.080 --> 18:21.830
After all, it was given
to my beloved consort by the Grand Tutor.

18:21.830 --> 18:22.440
I imagine

18:23.070 --> 18:24.800
it must be extremely valuable.

18:26.020 --> 18:27.070
I won't stop you.

18:28.030 --> 18:29.090
I'll even help you.

18:29.750 --> 18:31.810
Let's continue searching together.

18:39.680 --> 18:41.000
What's happening?

18:41.410 --> 18:42.790
Why all this commotion?

18:44.160 --> 18:45.160
Empress Dowager.

18:45.750 --> 18:46.560
I heard that

18:46.750 --> 18:49.510
Noble Consort Wei lost
an extremely precious jewelry.

18:49.510 --> 18:50.770
So early this morning,

18:50.930 --> 18:52.440
she went to Consort Yu's place

18:52.440 --> 18:53.440
to search for it.

18:54.200 --> 18:55.680
It's just a piece of jewelry.

18:55.680 --> 18:57.590
Is that worth making such a fuss?

18:58.550 --> 19:00.680
I also find it strange, Your Highness.

19:02.240 --> 19:04.240
Though the Consort's rank is high,

19:04.510 --> 19:06.110
she isn't actually favored.

19:06.550 --> 19:07.640
Yet His Majesty

19:07.960 --> 19:09.460
is willing to search the palace

19:09.460 --> 19:10.110
for her.

19:16.500 --> 19:19.500
You're saying this matter
even involved the Emperor?

19:19.590 --> 19:20.270
Yes.

19:22.310 --> 19:23.640
Something isn't right.

19:24.200 --> 19:25.830
Something's suspicious.

19:28.070 --> 19:28.930
Your Highness.

19:32.590 --> 19:33.880
How's it going on outside?

19:33.880 --> 19:35.210
I've found out, My Lady.

19:35.480 --> 19:36.160
Noble Consort Wei

19:36.160 --> 19:38.790
didn't find the red agate
in Consort Yu's quarters.

19:38.790 --> 19:39.920
They didn't find it?

19:43.110 --> 19:44.350
Are you certain you personally

19:44.350 --> 19:46.160
gave it to someone from her palace?

19:46.160 --> 19:47.360
Absolutely certain.

19:47.590 --> 19:49.200
I even saw that young eunuch

19:49.200 --> 19:50.830
enter Changning Palace with my own eyes.

19:50.830 --> 19:51.960
That's impossible.

19:53.400 --> 19:54.350
Oh, Your Highness.

19:54.350 --> 19:56.190
This food was sent by Consort Yu.

19:56.880 --> 19:58.680
Sending food at a time like this?

20:05.590 --> 20:06.450
Your Highness.

20:06.790 --> 20:07.550
Why would she

20:07.550 --> 20:08.920
only send steamed buns?

20:18.830 --> 20:19.230
How...

20:19.480 --> 20:19.880
How...

20:20.440 --> 20:22.240
How did the red agate end up here?

20:22.830 --> 20:24.030
Was this food box sent

20:24.170 --> 20:25.570
before the palace search

20:26.440 --> 20:27.550
or after?

20:28.000 --> 20:29.380
Shortly after the search.

20:29.380 --> 20:30.110
Are you sure?

20:30.400 --> 20:31.200
I'm certain.

20:31.640 --> 20:32.880
The guards had just left.

20:32.880 --> 20:34.080
I was quite flustered

20:34.400 --> 20:36.930
and almost dropped the box
when receiving it.

20:38.590 --> 20:40.650
If this box was sent after the search,

20:41.640 --> 20:43.770
it means she wasn't trying to frame me.

20:45.070 --> 20:46.930
It also shows she knows I did this.

20:47.240 --> 20:49.030
Yet, not only didn't she report me,

20:49.030 --> 20:50.230
she even returned it.

20:51.590 --> 20:53.400
Could it be that when she came last time,

20:53.400 --> 20:55.460
she genuinely wanted to befriend me?

20:56.510 --> 20:57.590
A 2D character

20:57.830 --> 21:00.070
couldn't possibly be this magnanimous.

21:00.070 --> 21:00.730
Or perhaps,

21:01.030 --> 21:02.880
because I changed the original storyline,

21:02.880 --> 21:04.350
a butterfly effect was caused?

21:04.350 --> 21:05.880
She never had the chance
to fall in love with Prince Duan,

21:05.880 --> 21:08.410
so she never had the opportunity
to turn evil.

21:08.510 --> 21:08.840
Wait.

21:09.550 --> 21:10.880
If she didn't turn evil,

21:11.000 --> 21:12.790
then the biggest villain in this story

21:12.790 --> 21:14.190
would be me, wouldn't it?

21:14.720 --> 21:15.510
Your Highness.

21:15.510 --> 21:16.400
What should we do

21:16.400 --> 21:18.200
with this red agate now?

21:42.750 --> 21:44.350
I've summoned all ministers today

21:44.350 --> 21:45.030
to ask about

21:45.680 --> 21:46.790
the preparations

21:47.240 --> 21:49.100
for the Grand Longevity Banquet.

21:52.590 --> 21:53.920
May I ask, Your Majesty,

21:54.160 --> 21:56.820
are you referring to last year's
or this year's?

21:57.200 --> 21:58.530
This year's, of course.

21:58.880 --> 22:00.400
Your Majesty's birthday from last year

22:00.400 --> 22:01.590
was just over a month ago.

22:01.590 --> 22:02.790
This year's Grand Longevity Banquet

22:02.240 --> 22:05.410
[Chief of the State Ceremonial Bureau]

22:03.200 --> 22:04.060
has not yet been

22:04.270 --> 22:06.000
scheduled by us, Your Majesty.

22:12.590 --> 22:14.390
Seems like the Ministry of Rites

22:14.960 --> 22:16.220
is not doing anything.

22:20.000 --> 22:20.800
Your Majesty!

22:22.310 --> 22:23.110
Your Majesty.

22:23.110 --> 22:23.910
Your Majesty.

22:24.070 --> 22:25.470
The agate has been found.

22:37.920 --> 22:39.250
It's just a small agate.

22:40.440 --> 22:42.370
There's nothing special about it.

22:45.790 --> 22:47.250
Why does Noble Consort Wei

22:48.590 --> 22:50.110
value it so highly?

22:53.880 --> 22:55.410
Your Majesty doesn't know.

22:55.720 --> 22:57.250
It's not an ordinary agate.

22:57.550 --> 22:59.880
It's a sarira that the Qiang State

23:00.070 --> 23:01.550
specially presented to Your Majesty

23:01.550 --> 23:02.610
for your birthday.

23:03.440 --> 23:05.000
It's a priceless treasure.

23:08.000 --> 23:09.400
This was presented to me?

23:10.880 --> 23:12.480
Why haven't I seen it before?

23:12.790 --> 23:13.590
Your Majesty,

23:13.590 --> 23:14.680
I know all the gift records

23:14.680 --> 23:15.960
by heart.

23:16.270 --> 23:18.070
There's absolutely no mistake.

23:18.270 --> 23:18.730
This...

23:19.070 --> 23:19.880
Perhaps

23:20.200 --> 23:22.530
Your Majesty gave it to Noble Consort Wei?

23:22.790 --> 23:23.720
Grand Tutor Wei,

23:24.240 --> 23:25.110
did I

23:25.790 --> 23:27.270
give this to Noble Consort Wei?

23:27.270 --> 23:28.000
Impossible!

23:30.030 --> 23:30.830
Your Majesty,

23:31.030 --> 23:33.630
this couldn't possibly belong
to my daughter.

23:34.030 --> 23:34.720
Perhaps

23:35.070 --> 23:36.000
it looks similar

23:36.480 --> 23:38.640
and the palace servants made a mistake.

23:38.640 --> 23:39.700
If that's the case,

23:40.310 --> 23:42.960
let Noble Consort Wei
come and identify it herself.

23:42.960 --> 23:44.020
Yes, Your Majesty.

23:44.240 --> 23:45.770
I'll summon her right away.

23:49.590 --> 23:50.030
What?

23:51.960 --> 23:53.890
You're saying Noble Consort Wei's

23:54.030 --> 23:55.400
lost red agate

23:56.350 --> 23:58.200
was found in our pond?

23:59.030 --> 24:01.760
And it's a sarira bead
offered by the Qiang State?

24:01.920 --> 24:02.580
Yes.

24:02.750 --> 24:04.720
His Majesty was furious when he found out.

24:04.720 --> 24:06.850
I heard he's already ordered Eunuch An

24:06.920 --> 24:09.250
to bring Noble Consort Wei to identify it.

24:11.110 --> 24:12.040
This is not good.

24:13.110 --> 24:14.510
If Noble Consort Wei admits

24:14.510 --> 24:15.790
this is what she lost,

24:16.160 --> 24:18.070
then the crime of hiding tribute items

24:18.070 --> 24:20.800
could lead to
the execution of her entire family.

24:26.000 --> 24:27.000
Empress Dowager,

24:27.310 --> 24:29.770
if we don't stop this now,
it will be too late.

24:30.110 --> 24:30.680
No.

24:31.200 --> 24:32.200
Something's off.

24:35.790 --> 24:36.990
This tribute item was

24:37.440 --> 24:39.160
found in my quarters.

24:39.790 --> 24:42.640
Everyone at court knows
who Grand Tutor Wei is loyal to.

24:42.640 --> 24:44.110
If I go there now,

24:45.070 --> 24:46.830
wouldn't it basically be
announcing to everyone

24:46.830 --> 24:49.200
that I'm the mastermind behind this?

24:49.750 --> 24:51.950
Sorry for not realizing it beforehand.

24:53.550 --> 24:53.950
You...

24:54.440 --> 24:55.240
Oh, my God...

24:56.200 --> 24:56.730
These...

24:57.200 --> 24:58.200
These two guys are

24:58.590 --> 24:59.880
good for nothing

25:00.270 --> 25:01.640
but trouble.

25:02.070 --> 25:03.550
Fools! Fools!

25:10.830 --> 25:12.290
Greetings, Your Majesty.

25:13.400 --> 25:14.600
My dear, please rise.

25:15.240 --> 25:16.640
Thank you, Your Majesty.

25:21.310 --> 25:22.440
My dear, come and see

25:23.720 --> 25:24.850
if what I've found is

25:25.270 --> 25:26.880
what you lost.

25:36.400 --> 25:37.200
Your Majesty,

25:38.070 --> 25:39.880
this is indeed the agate I lost.

25:43.070 --> 25:44.880
Where did you find it, Your Majesty?

25:44.880 --> 25:47.340
In the pond
at the Empress Dowager's palace.

25:49.960 --> 25:50.720
How could that be?

25:50.720 --> 25:52.510
My dear, please look carefully.

25:52.510 --> 25:53.750
Don't mistake something

25:53.750 --> 25:55.410
that isn't yours for your own.

25:55.480 --> 25:56.810
How could I be mistaken?

25:57.030 --> 25:59.290
This was my birthday gift from my father.

25:59.640 --> 26:01.920
I had been wearing it all the time.

26:02.440 --> 26:03.510
This agate even has

26:03.800 --> 26:05.680
my childhood nickname
carved on its bottom.

26:05.680 --> 26:06.240
Shut up!

26:06.880 --> 26:07.920
You foolish girl!

26:08.960 --> 26:10.350
You don't even know

26:10.880 --> 26:11.790
when it was switched,

26:11.790 --> 26:13.850
yet you dare talk such nonsense here!

26:14.200 --> 26:15.400
As precious as this item is,

26:15.400 --> 26:16.640
how could it have been switched?

26:16.640 --> 26:18.500
Father, what on earth is going on?

26:19.720 --> 26:20.520
Your Majesty,

26:20.830 --> 26:23.440
I'd like to expose
Grand Tutor Wei's corruption.

26:23.440 --> 26:25.160
[Vice Minister Wu]

26:23.640 --> 26:25.550
He allowed his son to accept bribes

26:25.550 --> 26:26.680
and ride recklessly in the streets,

26:26.680 --> 26:28.440
killing a commoner
who was filing a petition!

26:28.440 --> 26:30.440
His crimes are too numerous to list.

26:30.680 --> 26:32.210
This is complete nonsense!

26:32.240 --> 26:33.670
Who put you up to this

26:33.790 --> 26:34.790
to frame me?

26:35.640 --> 26:36.510
If my son

26:36.920 --> 26:38.590
truly committed such serious crimes,

26:38.590 --> 26:39.030
I

26:39.270 --> 26:40.730
would never cover for him!

26:40.920 --> 26:41.720
Your Majesty,

26:41.720 --> 26:43.400
I'm telling the truth!

26:43.400 --> 26:44.400
Truth?

26:44.680 --> 26:45.680
Do you have evidence?

26:45.680 --> 26:46.400
I do.

26:47.870 --> 26:49.900
[I want to charge the Salt Inspector]

26:49.900 --> 26:51.930
[with selling Salt Transportation
and Sales Licenses for personal gain.]

26:51.030 --> 26:52.270
Blocked petitions,

26:52.680 --> 26:54.010
engaged in corruption,

26:54.750 --> 26:55.920
accepted bribes,

26:56.720 --> 26:58.400
and hoarded tribute items.

27:03.240 --> 27:04.170
Grand Tutor Wei,

27:04.550 --> 27:07.110
it seems that you're not content
with being my father-in-law.

27:07.110 --> 27:09.400
You even want my throne, huh?

27:13.270 --> 27:14.200
I wouldn't dare.

27:14.970 --> 27:16.460
[Mu Yun]

27:15.510 --> 27:16.310
Your Majesty,

27:16.920 --> 27:17.650
may I request

27:18.550 --> 27:20.410
the Empress Dowager's presence?

27:21.440 --> 27:22.440
I promise

27:23.110 --> 27:24.400
I will come clean.

27:25.590 --> 27:28.000
On my way here with Noble Consort Wei,

27:28.240 --> 27:30.680
I noticed the lights
in the Empress Dowager's palace were out.

27:30.680 --> 27:31.240
I think

27:31.480 --> 27:32.610
the Empress Dowager

27:33.270 --> 27:35.730
went to rest early
to avoid being disturbed.

27:37.720 --> 27:38.790
In that case,

27:39.070 --> 27:40.670
I have to send Grand Tutor Wei

27:41.440 --> 27:43.590
to the Court of Revision.

27:45.210 --> 27:48.040
[Yongyan Hall]

27:46.750 --> 27:48.080
That's total bullshit!

27:48.590 --> 27:51.400
Noble Consort Wei
wears that sarira agate every day.

27:51.400 --> 27:53.000
How could you not know about that?

27:53.000 --> 27:53.640
Stop!

27:54.400 --> 27:56.400
The way you talked was way too modern!

27:56.400 --> 27:58.330
Can you please stick to the script?

28:00.310 --> 28:01.750
You've revised it so many times.

28:01.750 --> 28:03.950
Who can remember all those lines, miss?

28:04.920 --> 28:06.590
It's my first time directing.

28:06.880 --> 28:08.140
I'm a bit nervous, too.

28:08.750 --> 28:09.410
No worries.

28:10.400 --> 28:11.350
I'm a CEO.

28:11.960 --> 28:13.270
Manipulating employees is

28:13.270 --> 28:14.330
easy-peasy for me.

28:15.350 --> 28:16.950
To deal with Grand Tutor Wei,

28:17.830 --> 28:19.760
I can simply improvise on the spot.

28:20.270 --> 28:21.270
What about Xu Yao?

28:21.310 --> 28:23.110
You must make sure he's present.

28:23.640 --> 28:25.440
He's so concerned about anything

28:25.440 --> 28:26.680
related to Senior Minister Xu.

28:26.680 --> 28:28.920
So he rushed to the Court of Revision
as soon as he

28:28.920 --> 28:29.830
got the news.

28:31.030 --> 28:31.760
That's good.

28:33.030 --> 28:34.590
Is Xu Yao really that important?

28:34.590 --> 28:35.550
Of course!

28:36.110 --> 28:38.910
In the original story,
he's a legendary minister.

28:39.030 --> 28:40.030
Only with his help

28:40.480 --> 28:41.880
can we defeat Prince Duan

28:42.200 --> 28:43.730
and make you a good emperor.

28:44.920 --> 28:45.550
Besides,

28:46.510 --> 28:48.240
that young man is so handsome.

28:49.200 --> 28:52.260
Can you bear to see him
deceived and utilized by others?

28:52.790 --> 28:53.750
I knew it.

28:54.480 --> 28:55.080
All right,

28:55.110 --> 28:56.030
since you're ready,

28:56.030 --> 28:57.090
you may set off now.

28:58.720 --> 28:59.680
Come on!

29:00.680 --> 29:01.960
What are you waiting for?

29:01.960 --> 29:02.360
Hurry!

29:02.750 --> 29:04.790
I'll wait for your good news
in the library.

29:04.790 --> 29:05.390
Good luck!

29:14.960 --> 29:15.760
Your Majesty.

29:20.270 --> 29:21.070
Your Majesty!

29:21.720 --> 29:22.780
I've been wronged!

29:23.400 --> 29:25.790
I was only focused
on easing your burdens, Your Majesty.

29:25.790 --> 29:28.830
It was those villains who set me up.

29:29.030 --> 29:29.960
Are you saying

29:30.270 --> 29:31.930
I've wronged you for the issue

29:31.960 --> 29:33.560
regarding the sarira agate?

29:33.590 --> 29:34.990
I wouldn't dare say that.

29:35.030 --> 29:35.760
It's just...

29:37.720 --> 29:41.200
It's just that there's more
behind the issue about that sarira agate.

29:41.200 --> 29:42.460
My son brought it home.

29:43.070 --> 29:45.000
My daughter liked its bright color

29:45.350 --> 29:46.280
and asked for it.

29:46.920 --> 29:49.030
I had no idea it was so valuable!

29:49.270 --> 29:50.030
I see.

29:51.640 --> 29:52.640
So everything was

29:53.590 --> 29:55.550
done by your son and daughter.

29:56.240 --> 29:56.570
Fine.

29:57.590 --> 29:59.250
I'll release you immediately

29:59.400 --> 30:00.930
and imprison them instead.

30:01.310 --> 30:02.720
That's not what I meant.

30:04.640 --> 30:05.720
Then you mean

30:07.270 --> 30:08.930
you did everything yourself?

30:10.110 --> 30:11.310
You deceived me?

30:12.110 --> 30:13.840
That's not what I meant either.

30:14.790 --> 30:17.920
Neither this nor that.

30:18.720 --> 30:20.880
Then how exactly
did today's incident happen?

30:20.880 --> 30:24.080
My daughter lost her jewelry
at a rather suspicious time.

30:27.110 --> 30:28.370
Also, Vice Minister Wu

30:28.720 --> 30:29.690
and the Capital Prefect

30:29.690 --> 30:31.030
[I want to charge the Salt Inspector]

30:30.110 --> 30:31.960
carried the so-called evidence with them.

30:31.030 --> 30:32.380
[with selling Salt Transportation
and Sales Licenses for personal gain.]

30:32.680 --> 30:34.680
Your Majesty, you wouldn't believe

30:35.000 --> 30:37.730
that they didn't plan this
in advance, would you?

30:45.680 --> 30:47.480
Then I'm even more confused now.

30:48.270 --> 30:50.440
Vice Minister Wu and the Capital Prefect

30:50.440 --> 30:52.300
have no regular contact with you.

30:52.440 --> 30:54.720
Why would they set up
such an elaborate trap

30:54.720 --> 30:55.550
to get you?

30:56.440 --> 30:57.200
Yeah!

30:59.000 --> 31:00.660
They all work for Prince Duan!

31:02.160 --> 31:03.020
Prince Duan...

31:03.920 --> 31:06.180
Could it be Prince Duan trying to harm me?

31:08.830 --> 31:10.890
Why would Prince Duan want to harm me?

31:14.510 --> 31:15.550
Do you know

31:17.440 --> 31:19.550
that among Prince Duan's counselors,

31:19.550 --> 31:21.010
there is one called Xu Yao?

31:21.200 --> 31:22.000
Xu Yao?

31:22.240 --> 31:23.240
He's still alive?

31:26.000 --> 31:26.720
Back then,

31:27.270 --> 31:28.930
Senior Minister Xu's case was

31:28.960 --> 31:30.560
orchestrated by you, right?

31:30.830 --> 31:31.240
Yes.

31:32.110 --> 31:33.040
But at that time,

31:33.270 --> 31:34.930
it was all Prince Duan's idea.

31:36.030 --> 31:37.160
What a coincidence.

31:38.550 --> 31:41.240
The hunting dog is cooked
after the rabbit is caught.

31:41.240 --> 31:43.770
The bow is put away
when the birds are all gone.

31:44.070 --> 31:45.240
He used you

31:45.350 --> 31:46.680
and then abandoned you,

31:47.160 --> 31:48.160
saving

31:49.070 --> 31:49.920
your enemy,

31:50.350 --> 31:50.960
Xu Yao.

31:52.000 --> 31:54.800
He also made Xu Yao see you
as his lifelong nemesis.

31:54.960 --> 31:56.350
My brother is

31:56.720 --> 31:57.590
so horrible.

31:58.440 --> 32:00.030
First, he used you

32:01.200 --> 32:03.060
to eliminate Senior Minister Xu.

32:03.680 --> 32:05.240
Then he used Xu Yao

32:06.200 --> 32:07.350
to get rid of you.

32:08.400 --> 32:10.350
He truly kept it fair to both sides

32:10.830 --> 32:12.960
like no one else in this world.

32:15.310 --> 32:16.110
I also know

32:16.790 --> 32:19.390
why you joined
the Empress Dowager's faction.

32:20.750 --> 32:22.610
You studied hard since childhood

32:22.680 --> 32:23.940
with lofty ambitions.

32:25.000 --> 32:25.480
But...

32:29.200 --> 32:31.060
Your talents went unrecognized.

32:36.160 --> 32:37.830
By chance,

32:38.510 --> 32:41.170
Prince Duan valued
me as someone with potential

32:41.310 --> 32:42.790
and gave me an opportunity.

32:42.790 --> 32:44.070
He privately persuaded me

32:44.070 --> 32:46.000
to impeach Senior Minister Xu

32:46.310 --> 32:47.570
and cooperate with him

32:47.640 --> 32:50.040
to fabricate flawless evidence of crimes.

32:51.400 --> 32:53.000
Fortune favors the bold.

32:53.640 --> 32:54.510
I won my gamble!

32:55.030 --> 32:57.440
I not only gained merit
with the Empress Dowager

32:57.440 --> 32:59.300
but also won Prince Duan's trust.

33:00.270 --> 33:01.070
From then on,

33:02.550 --> 33:04.030
my career soared.

33:05.590 --> 33:07.320
Among all the court officials,

33:07.550 --> 33:08.270
only you

33:09.400 --> 33:10.640
could play both sides

33:10.640 --> 33:11.840
with such stability.

33:13.110 --> 33:14.240
You've been working

33:14.960 --> 33:16.000
for both of them.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.830
Only I, the Emperor...

33:22.680 --> 33:23.160
I am

33:24.030 --> 33:26.440
so sinful and deserve to die.

33:32.680 --> 33:33.480
Your Majesty,

33:35.400 --> 33:36.400
I know

33:38.160 --> 33:39.690
that I can not survive this.

33:42.030 --> 33:43.030
I just want to know

33:44.030 --> 33:46.480
how you learned about this, Your Majesty.

33:59.830 --> 34:00.360
Stand up.

34:06.480 --> 34:07.340
I just guessed.

34:16.590 --> 34:17.960
Just guessed?

34:30.230 --> 34:31.090
Your Highness.

34:32.070 --> 34:32.800
How did Xu Yao

34:34.150 --> 34:35.880
get into the Court of Revision?

34:36.320 --> 34:37.320
According to the guards,

34:37.320 --> 34:39.250
he entered with an imperial token.

34:40.440 --> 34:42.000
Oh, Xu Yao...

34:43.800 --> 34:45.150
I'm afraid you're

34:46.400 --> 34:48.110
going to lose this game.

35:05.550 --> 35:06.280
Who's there?

35:07.840 --> 35:09.400
I need to see Her Highness
for something urgent.

35:09.400 --> 35:10.400
Without His Majesty's decree,

35:10.400 --> 35:11.860
no one is allowed to enter.

35:12.440 --> 35:13.300
Your Highness!

35:13.510 --> 35:14.370
Your Highness!

35:15.710 --> 35:16.440
Xu Yao?

35:17.030 --> 35:17.830
Why is he here?

35:18.320 --> 35:19.280
Let him in now.

35:19.800 --> 35:20.190
Yes.

35:23.280 --> 35:23.740
Please.

35:24.670 --> 35:25.480
Mr. Xu?

35:27.280 --> 35:28.480
What brings you here?

35:28.480 --> 35:29.340
Your Highness,

35:29.590 --> 35:31.840
I need to see His Majesty
for some urgent matters.

35:31.840 --> 35:34.100
Could you please help me, Your Highness?

35:34.160 --> 35:35.630
Mei, go invite His Majesty over.

35:35.630 --> 35:36.360
Understood.

35:41.070 --> 35:41.870
What's wrong?

35:42.280 --> 35:43.480
Is someone after you?

35:43.880 --> 35:44.610
Don't worry.

35:44.760 --> 35:45.760
You're absolutely safe here.

35:45.760 --> 35:46.620
Your Highness,

35:46.880 --> 35:48.010
it's really urgent.

35:49.070 --> 35:50.630
If it's about Senior Minister Xu,

35:50.630 --> 35:51.890
I think I know about it.

35:53.510 --> 35:56.190
Your Highness,
you truly have His Majesty's favor.

35:56.190 --> 35:57.320
I was investigating

35:57.510 --> 35:59.440
my father's wrongful conviction.

35:59.710 --> 36:02.320
I found all the evidence
pointed to Prince Duan all of a sudden.

36:02.320 --> 36:02.850
Just now,

36:03.440 --> 36:04.570
I returned to my room

36:04.760 --> 36:05.890
and took a sip of tea.

36:06.670 --> 36:08.270
I noticed a weird taste, felt

36:08.400 --> 36:10.000
a burning pain in my stomach,

36:10.840 --> 36:12.440
and realized I was poisoned.

36:13.440 --> 36:14.500
You were poisoned?

36:14.550 --> 36:15.880
Let's go find the imperial physician.

36:15.880 --> 36:16.590
Your Highness,

36:16.590 --> 36:19.630
since Prince Duan wants me dead,
I have no chance of survival.

36:19.630 --> 36:20.150
So,

36:20.800 --> 36:22.400
I pretended to know nothing,

36:22.400 --> 36:24.110
snuck out through the back door,

36:24.110 --> 36:27.170
and temporarily escaped
Prince Duan's secret guards.

36:27.280 --> 36:28.960
With no way to meet His Majesty,

36:28.960 --> 36:30.360
I could only come to the library

36:30.360 --> 36:32.360
to ask for your help, Your Highness.

36:35.030 --> 36:35.440
Xu Yao!

36:39.110 --> 36:40.440
I know my sins are grave.

36:42.030 --> 36:44.290
But before I die, I have only one request.

36:44.480 --> 36:46.280
I've worked for Prince Duan for years,

36:46.280 --> 36:47.800
and I know all his crimes.

36:49.550 --> 36:51.410
If His Majesty can save my father,

36:51.510 --> 36:52.040
I, Xu Yao,

36:53.480 --> 36:55.340
will surely repay this kindness!

36:55.920 --> 36:56.650
Don't worry.

36:57.110 --> 36:58.760
His Majesty is a man of his word.

36:58.760 --> 37:02.090
Senior Minister Xu is already on his way
back to the capital.

37:02.190 --> 37:02.920
Is that true?

37:07.550 --> 37:08.610
That's wonderful.

37:09.800 --> 37:10.330
My father

37:11.400 --> 37:12.280
has always hoped

37:12.280 --> 37:14.230
that His Majesty could be a good emperor.

37:14.230 --> 37:15.030
If he returns,

37:15.630 --> 37:16.960
he will certainly serve
with absolute loyalty,

37:16.960 --> 37:18.880
using all his knowledge
to assist His Majesty,

37:18.880 --> 37:20.030
making His Majesty...

37:20.030 --> 37:20.440
Xu Yao!

37:22.110 --> 37:23.070
Don't worry.

37:24.070 --> 37:26.000
His Majesty values
Senior Minister Xu's talents greatly,

37:26.000 --> 37:27.530
and he values yours as well.

37:27.630 --> 37:28.480
Also, His Majesty

37:28.480 --> 37:30.360
has already arranged a way out for you.

37:30.360 --> 37:32.360
He wants you to safely switch sides.

37:32.400 --> 37:33.840
Let's get out of here first, alright?

37:33.840 --> 37:34.370
Let's go.

37:34.760 --> 37:35.360
I'm afraid

37:36.070 --> 37:38.270
I won't be able to see His Majesty today.

37:41.250 --> 37:41.900
[Library]

37:57.670 --> 37:59.760
Fire! Come and help put it out!

38:00.030 --> 38:01.360
Someone please help!

38:04.960 --> 38:05.690
It's on fire?

38:05.960 --> 38:06.490
Let's go!

38:06.760 --> 38:08.160
Let's get out of here now!

38:08.630 --> 38:09.090
Come on.

38:11.480 --> 38:11.680
Go.

38:21.320 --> 38:21.720
Xu Yao!

38:24.550 --> 38:25.070
Get up!

38:25.110 --> 38:25.970
Your Highness,

38:26.110 --> 38:26.910
it's too late.

38:27.070 --> 38:28.110
I've recorded all

38:28.110 --> 38:29.590
of Prince Duan's plans in a book

38:29.590 --> 38:32.030
and buried it under the window
of his mansion's back kitchen.

38:32.030 --> 38:33.590
Don't go looking for it right away.

38:33.590 --> 38:34.960
Wait at least 7 days.

38:35.070 --> 38:35.880
Stop this talk.

38:35.880 --> 38:36.910
Let's get out first.

38:36.910 --> 38:37.440
Let's go.

38:48.230 --> 38:48.760
Xu Yao!

38:51.510 --> 38:52.030
Run.

38:53.110 --> 38:55.170
Don't look back for whoever you meet.

38:56.800 --> 38:57.630
Stay alive.

38:58.360 --> 38:58.840
Xu Yao!

38:59.710 --> 39:00.570
Get up quickly!

39:03.710 --> 39:04.140
Xu Yao,

39:04.510 --> 39:05.440
get up now!

39:08.320 --> 39:10.370
This isn't how your story ends
in the book.

39:10.370 --> 39:12.860
♪ In the time and space of chaos ♪

39:11.400 --> 39:12.480
Don't you remember?

39:12.480 --> 39:13.680
You still have a vendetta to settle.

39:13.680 --> 39:16.700
♪ Every time I open my eyes ♪

39:14.190 --> 39:15.120
You're so young.

39:15.360 --> 39:17.410
You must have many things
you still want to do.

39:17.410 --> 39:20.610
♪ Your silhouette is engraved inside ♪

39:17.550 --> 39:19.750
Are you really willing to die like this?

39:20.270 --> 39:21.880
Smooth talkers

39:22.280 --> 39:24.280
often disguise themselves
as someone loyal and virtuous.

39:23.790 --> 39:26.530
♪ Then we transform ♪

39:25.190 --> 39:27.000
Those who are truly honest and sincere

39:27.000 --> 39:29.800
may be clumsy in words,
but they act with integrity.

39:27.170 --> 39:30.230
♪ Into the blazing light to guard ♪

39:30.560 --> 39:32.840
So one must discern right from wrong.

39:30.610 --> 39:35.240
♪ Our eternal galaxy ♪

39:33.110 --> 39:35.310
One move can secure the nation's peace.

39:36.070 --> 39:37.030
Repeat after me.

39:36.110 --> 39:38.450
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

39:39.270 --> 39:41.880
♪ And let time freeze ♪

39:39.550 --> 39:40.360
One move

39:40.630 --> 39:42.360
can secure the nation's peace.

39:42.590 --> 39:48.320
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

39:46.480 --> 39:50.280
Secure the nation's peace.

39:48.720 --> 39:50.010
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

39:50.690 --> 39:53.540
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

39:54.030 --> 39:54.480
Xu Yao...

39:54.070 --> 39:55.750
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

39:55.770 --> 40:01.660
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

39:57.670 --> 39:58.280
Xu Yao!

39:58.880 --> 40:00.070
Don't give up!

40:02.210 --> 40:03.670
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

40:04.140 --> 40:07.050
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

40:06.440 --> 40:07.280
Xu Yao!

40:07.520 --> 40:09.660
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

40:09.760 --> 40:11.290
♪ We can dance together ♪

40:10.480 --> 40:11.400
Xu Yao!

40:11.310 --> 40:20.910
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

40:43.610 --> 40:46.150
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

40:47.070 --> 40:49.490
♪ And let time freeze ♪

40:50.200 --> 40:55.970
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

40:56.390 --> 40:57.470
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

40:58.040 --> 41:00.860
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

41:01.490 --> 41:03.060
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

41:03.080 --> 41:09.080
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

41:09.680 --> 41:11.330
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

41:11.640 --> 41:14.510
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

41:14.990 --> 41:17.100
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

41:17.120 --> 41:18.760
♪ We can dance together ♪

41:18.790 --> 41:27.860
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

41:29.570 --> 41:35.520
♪ Never looking back ♪

41:54.280 --> 41:54.880
Lady Yu?

42:02.630 --> 42:03.160
Yong'er.

42:06.150 --> 42:06.800
Help me.

42:10.150 --> 42:11.610
Take me to see His Majesty.

42:24.550 --> 42:25.080
Let's go.

42:28.800 --> 42:29.770
Stay here and wait for me.

42:29.770 --> 42:31.700
I'll have someone carry you there.

42:31.710 --> 42:32.070
No.

42:33.590 --> 42:34.450
Don't leave me.

42:37.630 --> 42:38.490
Don't leave me.

42:41.800 --> 42:42.800
Your Highnesses.

43:02.400 --> 43:03.930
Greetings, Your Highness.

43:04.880 --> 43:06.680
I heard the library caught fire.

43:07.000 --> 43:09.130
I've sent my guards to put out the fire.

43:09.360 --> 43:12.360
Fortunately, Her Highness is blessed
with good luck.

43:18.400 --> 43:19.660
Are you hurt anywhere,

43:21.110 --> 43:22.960
Your Highness?

43:35.150 --> 43:36.010
Your Highness,

43:36.840 --> 43:38.770
I don't think this is appropriate.

43:38.770 --> 43:39.830
It's an emergency.

43:40.760 --> 43:43.760
I'm simply escorting Her Highness
back to the palace.

43:49.550 --> 43:50.410
Your Highness!

43:54.510 --> 43:55.510
Let me go with you.

43:56.000 --> 43:57.510
No need for help here.

43:58.960 --> 44:01.960
Please fetch the imperial physician,
Your Highness.

44:06.550 --> 44:07.150
All right.

44:21.480 --> 44:24.010
Why are you trembling so much,
Your Highness?

44:24.880 --> 44:26.340
Are you scared of heights,

44:26.760 --> 44:29.020
worried about falling down these steps?

44:29.110 --> 44:30.110
If you're scared,

44:31.510 --> 44:33.110
you can hold onto me tightly.

44:34.110 --> 44:35.240
It's just the gusts.

44:36.190 --> 44:37.920
They're making me feel chilly.

44:39.280 --> 44:41.540
Your Highness, I hope you and I can remain

44:41.710 --> 44:43.240
as we were when we first met,

44:43.920 --> 44:45.000
without fear,

44:46.320 --> 44:47.480
without distance.

44:51.760 --> 44:52.480
Do you know

44:53.230 --> 44:55.890
serving the emperor is
like living with a tiger?

44:56.230 --> 44:57.760
Instead of fearing me,

44:59.440 --> 45:01.230
you should fear His Majesty.

45:07.590 --> 45:08.800
That's much better.

45:11.280 --> 45:14.940
After all, Grand Tutor Wei's collusion
with the Salt Inspector is

45:15.030 --> 45:18.000
an open secret throughout the court.

45:19.030 --> 45:21.090
Yet His Majesty has kept ignoring it.

45:22.800 --> 45:24.660
To exonerate the Salt Inspector,

45:25.320 --> 45:27.850
they've exploited
the common people and sold

45:27.880 --> 45:32.210
Salt Transportation and Sales Licenses
privately to line their own pockets,

45:33.670 --> 45:36.200
while the people
who wrote petitions in blood

45:37.070 --> 45:39.280
could only die from their lashings.

45:42.110 --> 45:42.970
Your Highness,

45:43.630 --> 45:44.480
this world

45:46.000 --> 45:48.200
has suffered from tyranny for too long.

45:52.590 --> 45:54.990
What are you talking about, Your Highness?

45:55.150 --> 45:56.710
I don't understand.

45:57.840 --> 45:58.440
Let her go!

46:20.940 --> 46:21.730
♪ Tell me ♪

46:22.450 --> 46:25.900
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

46:27.520 --> 46:28.580
♪ Walk past me ♪

46:28.980 --> 46:32.730
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

46:34.160 --> 46:36.580
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

46:37.500 --> 46:40.150
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

46:41.010 --> 46:43.970
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

46:43.990 --> 46:46.150
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

46:46.550 --> 46:49.000
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

46:49.050 --> 46:50.810
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

46:50.840 --> 46:53.360
♪ I never yielded ♪

46:53.670 --> 46:55.110
♪ But why ♪

46:55.400 --> 46:59.860
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

47:00.300 --> 47:02.620
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

47:02.710 --> 47:04.560
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

47:04.590 --> 47:06.910
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

47:05.000 --> 47:05.480
Sorry,

47:07.280 --> 47:07.880
I'm late.

47:07.330 --> 47:09.060
♪ The first time I met you ♪

47:09.460 --> 47:17.280
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪
